snippet.title: Longplay of Harry Obby 0.9.0  | No Deaths | Chapter 1-10 + Unlocking Lord Voldemort
snippet.description:
Download Harry Obby: https://gamejolt.com/games/harryobby/349899

What's up, dudes! I am the creator of Harry Obby. This video shows you the way to beat this game.

New Features of version 0.9.0:
A picture of Jim Pickens has been added to the game because Kevin has played Harry Obby. (Btw, thank you, Kevin! I am your fan. I love your Roleplay videos.)
You will not lose your cards after you die.
I added some UI texts to tell the player about the objective.
I added a few light objects.

By the way, this game will not have any big changes and I think it is better to focus on making a new game or a spin-off game of Harry Obby.
